---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import { Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 mx-auto place-items-center">
  <!-- REST API  -->
  <div
    class="max-w-sm mx-4 mb-4 border rounded-lg shadow bg-gray-800 border-gray-700"
  >
    <a href="https://anime-api-xi.vercel.app/" target="_blank">
      <img class="rounded-t-lg" src="/images/JikanAPI.png" alt="" />
    </a>
    <div class="p-5">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="React" />
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="Javascript" />
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="TailwindCss" />
      </div>
      <a href="https://anime-api-xi.vercel.app/" target="_blank">
        <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          Anime (API) Database Search
        </h5>
      </a>
      <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-400">
        A React app I made using a REST API called Jikan, containing JSON
        information about shows from Japan. I utilized 'useState' from React as
        well as async, fetch, await. Creating a search function parsing through
        the JSON data, returning 15 related shows, each within a card with their
        own synopsis and cover image.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://anime-api-xi.vercel.app/"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-blue-800"
      >
        Visit the Site
        <svg
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 -mr-1"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          ><path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ExpressOwl/animeAPI"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-blue-800"
      >
        GitHub Repo
        <svg
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="w-4 h-4 ml-2 -mr-1"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          ><path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- REST API  -->

  <!-- Pearl China -->
  <div
    class="max-w-sm mx-4 mb-4 border rounded-lg shadow bg-gray-800 border-gray-700"
  >
    <a href="https://www.pearlchina.co.uk/" target="_blank">
      <img class="rounded-t-lg" src="/images/PearlChina.png" alt="" />
    </a>
    <div class="p-5">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="HTML" />
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="Vite" />
        <Icon class="w-11 h-11 mx-3" name="TailwindCss" />
      </div>
      <a href="https://www.pearlchina.co.uk/" target="_blank">
        <h5 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          Pearl China (Online Menu)
        </h5>
      </a>
      <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-400">
        Client wanted a mobile site which will hold their ever updating menu and
        prices. The site has a Google Map Embed and uses grid layout for the
        menus for a responsive experience. This site taught me how to include
        favicons for all browsers. It is hosted on Vercel via CloudFlare and
        gets a humble 1000 vists a week.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.pearlchina.co.uk/"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-blue-800"
      >
        Visit the Site
