          My Portfolio / Blog
        </h5>
      </a>
      <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-400">
        This portfolio site is made using AstroJS. I learnt the convenience of
        reuseable components and how folder structure is important in order to
        make code readable and maintainable. This project also taught me how to
        use GIT and its version control system, as well as reading of the
        documentations in order to properly implement dependencies.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ExpressOwl/Ramblings"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-blue-800"
